---

<div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary-800 mb-4">Ingrese los detalles del envío</h3>
    
    <div class="space-y-4">
      <div>
        <label for="direccion-origen" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1">Dirección de origen</label>
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="absolute inset-y-0 left-0 pl-3 flex items-center pointer-events-none">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-gray-400" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5.05 4.05a7 7 0 119.9 9.9L10 18.9l-4.95-4.95a7 7 0 010-9.9zM10 11a2 2 0 100-4 2 2 0 000 4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <input 
            type="text" 
            id="direccion-origen" 
            class="block w-full pl-10 pr-3 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md shadow-sm focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-500 focus:border-primary-500" 
            placeholder="Ej: Av. Colón 2850"
          >
        </div>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1">Ingrese la dirección donde se recogerá el paquete</p>
      </div>
      
      <div>
        <label for="direccion-destino" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1">Dirección de destino</label>
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="absolute inset-y-0 left-0 pl-3 flex items-center pointer-events-none">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-gray-400" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5.05 4.05a7 7 0 119.9 9.9L10 18.9l-4.95-4.95a7 7 0 010-9.9zM10 11a2 2 0 100-4 2 2 0 000 4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <input 
            type="text" 
            id="direccion-destino" 
            class="block w-full pl-10 pr-3 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md shadow-sm focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-500 focus:border-primary-500" 
            placeholder="Ej: Av. Independencia 1546"
          >
        </div>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1">Ingrese la dirección donde se entregará el paquete</p>
      </div>

      
      <button 
        id="calcular-btn"
        class="w-full bg-secondary-500 hover:bg-secondary-600 text-white font-medium py-2 px-4 rounded-md shadow transition duration-150 ease-in-out focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-secondary-500"
      >
        Calcular precio
      </button>
    </div>
    
    <div class="mt-6 border-t border-gray-200 pt-4">
      <h4 class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">Información adicional:</h4>
      <ul class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-1">
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <svg class="h-4 w-4 text-success-500 mr-1.5 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
          </svg>
          Horario de entrega: Lun-Vie 10hs a 18hs
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <svg class="h-4 w-4 text-success-500 mr-1.5 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
          </svg>
          Cobertura en toda la ciudad
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <svg class="h-4 w-4 text-success-500 mr-1.5 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
          </svg>
          Pagos en efectivo, transferencia o billeteras virtuales
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>